column1: ConditionsEvent/Operation:Permit Linear Footage15840Elements of OccupancyPlacing aerial strand along 24th and 25th avenues.Will involve driving a truck from pole to pole andstopping at each pole for 30 minutes at a time.From:9/14/2015 07:00:00 AMStart Time7:00AMTo:9/25/2015 05:00:00 PMEnd Time05:00:00 PMNeed to call for InspectionNeed to post tow-away signTo activate and register this permit for towing, call(415) 554-5824 a minimum of 72 hours prior tooccupancy.  To tow a vehicle call the Tow Desk at(415) 553-1200.Special Traffic permit requiredNFood:NOther:Performing Arts:NStreet Space Hours7:00AM Thru 05:00:00 PMMeter Segment(s)Night Noise
